since 1970 cambodia has suffered a devastating fiveyear civil 
war a reign of terror by the chinesebacked communist khmer rouge 
from 1975 to 1978 a 1978 vietnamese invasion and a continuing 
guerrilla war against the vietnamesebacked government 
millions of people have been killed in the turmoil 
