strength and weight loss not maximum performance squires said 
children are unusually susceptible overuse injuries from 
exercise without proper conditioning and training said dr lyle 
micheli an orthopedist and director of sports medicine at 
childrens hospital in boston 
is running good for kids absolutely he said is too much 
running bad for kids absolutely the question is how much is too 
much 
 
</TEXT>
</DOC>

