campaigns were less than effective the company also faces stiff 
competition in its consumer foods business 
under smiths leadership general foods also has suffered 
lagging growth and earnings you cant say his track record at 
general foods would lend itself to any wideeyed enthusiasm 
froelich said 
much of general foods difficulites can be linked to its core 
maxwell house coffee business which is suffering from lackluster 
growth but analysts point to other potential problems 
