said the proposed acquisition would be a major step in 
expanding fleetnorstars new england banking franchise 
he noted that fleetnorstar already has four norstar banks in 
new york state and operates merrillnorstar bank in maine united 
bank in connecticut and fleet national bank in rhodse island 
j terrence murray president of fleetnorstar said that after 
the acquisition it is expected that james chandler will continue 
as indian heads chairman and he harrington jr will continue as 
its president and chief executive 
harrington said he expects the bank to operate as an 
autonomous unit of fleetnorstar after the transaction is 
completed we do not see any significant cahnges for the next few 
years he said 
fleetnorstar financial group is a diversified national 
financial services company with about 1000 offices in 40 states 
